            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/10/205556113/f3b04e3ddf6e07cf676d9d163168ebce_838966176078489183.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Bond of Life is a mechanic that applies a status on the character. The status is indicated by the red bar on the character’s HP bar and a symbol.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Bond of Life prevents characters from recovering HP for a long duration (600s) or until the status is cleared by healing the character for an amount equal to the Bond of Life applied. If another Bond of Life is applied to the character before it is cleared, it will stack with the existing Bond of Life. The maximum amount of Bond of Life is 200% of the character Max HP.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Characters can be healed by: Statue of the Seven/Underwater Recovery Orbs, Healing Food, character/party’s healing abilities.",
